00:00:28.980 --> 00:00:32.370
Do I need to go?

00:00:32.470 --> 00:00:36.880
Still, my nurse instincts tell me to go,

00:00:36.900 --> 00:00:42.290
I grabbed my bag and went to see him,

00:00:42.310 --> 00:00:46.450
